Installation:

git clone git://github.com/mschinz/vimfiles.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

cd ~/.vim
git submodule init
git submodule update

on MS Windows: New-Symlink ~/vimfiles ~/.vim

